 12px; background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; height: auto; width: auto; clear: both; padding: 0px;\" src=\"http://www.yangchanglu.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E7%9C%81%E9%A6%96%E6%89%B9%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E6%9A%A8%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E5%91%98%E5%9F%B9%E8%AE%AD%E7%8F%AD.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[10466,20534],"tags":[8635,11986,18013]}